title: Revisit Filter Questions
set-jump: 31_fq_result

Facilyn: If you skipped any checks, you can revisit them now. Otherwise, you can finalize your decision.

- #revisit_skips

@revisit_cause
title: Revisit Cause and Effect Check
on-arrival: achvm_last = "Filter Navigator" if achievement_filter_navigator = 0
achievement: filter_navigator
view-if: fltr_cause = "Skipped"
tags: revisit_skips

Me: Revisit Cause and Effect Check.

Facilyn: "Does this action address the root cause of the problem?"

- #cause_effect

@revisit_weak_link
title: Revisit the Weak Link Checks
on-arrival: achvm_last = "Filter Navigator" if achievement_filter_navigator = 0
achievement: filter_navigator
view-if: wl_social = "Skipped" or wl_biological = "Skipped" or wl_financial = "Skipped"
tags: revisit_skips

Me: Revisit the Weak Link Checks.

Facilyn: Which type of weak link would you like to check?

- #weak_links

@revisit_marginal
title: Revisit Marginal Reaction Check
on-arrival: achvm_last = "Filter Navigator" if achievement_filter_navigator = 0
achievement: filter_navigator
view-if: fltr_marginal = "Skipped"
tags: revisit_skips

Me: Revisit Marginal Reaction Check.

Facilyn: "Which action will provide the greatest return toward the goal for each additional unit of money or time invested?"

- #marginal_reaction

@revisit_gross_profit
